item.description:
Sponsored by Mass Bay Road Club

Meet: Sunday April 25th @ 8:30 - Norwell High School, 18 South Street, Norwell, MA

30 mile route goes through Norwell, Hanover, Pembroke and Marshfield

50 mile route adds Scituate, Green Harbor and Humarock

Helmets are required

Open ride - no fee or club membership required - all riders at all levels are welcome and cue sheets are provided.

I will be outside of a gray Ford Escape with a white road bike.
